= master / unreleased

  * Add event-handling capabilities to outbound listener [Harry Vangberg]

  * New method for starting listeners, which given a block provides some sugar
    for starting multiple listeners. FSR.start_ies! and FSR.start_oes! has been
    deprecated. [Harry Vangberg]

  * `api` now has the same state-machine approach as applications
    [Harry Vangberg]

